==Inventory==
*3–4 [[Blighted super restore]] potions (or [[Prayer potion|prayer potions]])
*1 [[super energy]] or [[stamina potion]] (optional)
*[[Imbued heart|Imbued]]/[[saturated heart]] (optional if using a powered staff, replaces tormented bracelet)
*[[Runes]] to cast [[Iban Blast]] if using [[Iban's staff]]
*Food ([[lobsters]] or better)
*A [[looting bag]], be aware you will drop any items within the looting bag should you die, regardless of the value of the items
*A teleport that works up to level 30 Wilderness, such as a [[royal seed pod]], [[Amulet of glory (6)|charged amulet of glory]], or [[Slayer ring]].

